

# 🧠 Master Module 01: Adaptability & Resilience

This folder contains a comprehensive breakdown of the 32 lessons within the McKinsey Forward Adaptability & Resilience module. It documents my journey from a Fixed to a Growth mindset, focusing on sustainable high performance.

## 📌 Module Roadmap
The course is built on the **Three Drivers of Adaptability**:
1. **Activate Learning:** Building high-velocity learning habits.
2. **Strengthen Resilience:** Managing energy and emotional well-being.
3. **Reinforce with Purpose:** Aligning work with personal and organizational goals.

