## 🧠 Key Topic Breakdowns

### 01. Activate Learning
- **Mindset Shifts:** Moving from "I can't do this" to "I can't do this *yet*."
- **Feedback Loops:** Using the "Plus/Delta" model to evaluate startup pivots at Quantum Park.

### 02. Strengthen Resilience
- **Energy Management:** Categorizing tasks by Energy Drain vs. Energy Gain.
- **The Resilience Scale:** Tracking my ability to bounce back from technical failures or rejected proposals.

### 03. Reinforce with Purpose
- **The Purpose Compass:** Aligning my C++ development and AI research with the mission of improving education-to-work pipelines in Pakistan.

